longBusinessSummary: Onyx Acquisition Co. I does not have significant operations. The company focuses on effecting a merger, share exchange, asset acquisition, share purchase, reorganization, or similar business combination with one or more businesses or entities. It intends to focus on construction technology and general industrials. The company was formerly known as Jumpball Construction Tech. Onyx Acquisition Co. I was incorporated in 2021 and is based in New York, New York.
